name: The Crystal Forest of Enlightenment
description:
She glowed amidst the darkness that engulfed her. I had just followed the light. Was I lost? Was she?
The radiance was bedazzling. It felt like dream. I had reached the ends of my mind to conjure up the forest of enlightenment. It felt familiar, but something was amiss. Was this the metaphysical? Had I reached the metaverse of spirituality?

Or maybe just enjoy the artwork as a wallpaper, a cover pic, or a digital print.
1920 x 1080 px Genesis Drop. 20 Editions only. An artwork by rdTect
